      "role": "user",
      "content": "so you're basically saying the \"consensus\" is that we should just accept these industries failing and then try to fix the wreckage with safety nets? it sounds like you're saying protectionism is just fundamentally wrong/inefficient and the only \"correct\" answer is to stick to free trade and deal with the fallout later.",
